 economics of biomass production in the United States (1995) Proceedings of the Second Biomass Conference of the Americas: Energy, Environment, Agriculture, and Industry, pp. 1314-1323. , NREL/CP-200-8098, National Renewable Energy Laboratory, Portland, OR; Nienow, S., McNamara, K., Gillespie, A., Assessing plantation biomass for co-firing with coal in northern Indiana: A linear programming approach (2000) Biomass and Bioenergy, 18, pp. 125-135; Perlack, R., Wright, L., Huston, M., Schramm, W., (1995) Biomass Fuel from Woody Crops for Electricity Power Generation, , ORNL-6871. US Department of Energy Oak Ridge National Laboratory, TN","Gan, J.; Department of Forest Science, Texas A and M University, College Station, TX 77843-2135, United States; email: j-gan@silva.tamu.edu",,,,,,,,09619534,,BMSBE,,"English","Biomass Bioenergy",Conference Paper,Scopus,2-s2.0-33644885291
